1.2.0.name: drupal/warmer_cdn

security-coverage.message: Covered by Drupal's security advisory policy

1.2.0.description: Executes HTTP requests to warm the edge caches. It is useful without a CDN as well, as it will also warm Varnish and Page Cache.
